{"tid":1683001,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇左Call me by your name 續集Find me?","createTime":"2019-10-30T11:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T11:51:57.000Z","uid":90315,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d37fae4235d355e69761fde8e948d37651c3990c","tid":1683001,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"講緊小說<br />\n琴日出左<br />\n<br />\n佢地<br />\n佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">係埋一齊了</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.macmillan.com/folio-assets/macmillan_us_frontbookcovers_1000H/9780374155018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.macmillan.com%2Ffolio-assets%2Fmacmillan_us_frontbookcovers_1000H%2F9780374155018.jpg&h=ad150d3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95a7a8bef0141dd1740f794654cc8fc0a519947c","tid":1683001,"uid":45280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b279f9bcc5e65ee960552659612f370eed3fdc1","tid":1683001,"uid":90315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"佳句摘錄<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote> <br />\n<br />\nOliver: <br />\n&ldquo;If he asks how long I&rsquo;m staying, I&rsquo;ll tell him the truth. If he asks where I plan to sleep, I&rsquo;ll tell him the truth. If he asks. But he won&rsquo;t ask. He won&rsquo;t have to. He knows.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nElio:<br />\n&ldquo;We knew things were going to be different but we couldn&rsquo;t quite grasp how the wish to run headlong into what we&rsquo;d once had years before could stir our reluctance to be in bed together.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\nElio:<br />\n&ldquo;He knew that if neither of us sought out the other it was only because we had never really parted and that, regardless of where we were, who we were with, and whatever stood in our way, all he needed when the time was right was simply to come and find me.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e8f03f9a6f8fb5f29186e8db1e4fa452aed78e64","tid":1683001,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"Elio Elio Elio<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461600dd7f7cdc84c86730c0446f32e5fa2f4e33","tid":1683001,"uid":90315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e8f03f9a6f8fb5f29186e8db1e4fa452aed78e64","tid":1683001,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"Elio Elio Elio<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/9DaWHruhoEtkAEGjuG/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9DaWHruhoEtkAEGjuG%2Fgiphy.gif&h=af5003a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b96c9f7516d660ae30c04308209d51f117beb140","tid":1683001,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"CNBYN原本嗰本我買咗<br />\n都未開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁快又寫本新"},{"pid":"24903d70ffdb6a14dd324fcbe80b34c44b2b7968","tid":1683001,"uid":91189,"like":0,"dislike"